720360f-a.title: Manhattan: Henry Street - Catherine Street
720360f-a.text:
Henry Street, north side, east from and including Catharine, to Market
Streets. Also shown is a portion of the Manhattan Bridge, in the back-
ground.
September 5, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
